DOCUMENTATION

  doc/imbw-paper-en.txt française 
  doc/imbw-paper-fr.txt english
  doc/imbw-paper-it.txt italiano

COMPILATION

  $ ./configure
  you can enable debugging through the --enable-debug flag
  $ make
  the libimbw/ directory contains everything you'll need

compiled/tested on:

  Red Hat Linux release 8.0 (Psyche)
  SlackWare 8.0.0 (åtta)

